sequenceDiagram
    participant Hook as "Hook Script"
    participant Queue as "memory-queue.jsonl"
    participant Processor as "drain-queue.sh"
    participant CLI as "npx mcp-automem queue"
    participant Client as "AutoMemClient"
    participant API as "AutoMem API"
    
    Note over Hook,Queue: Event Capture Phase
    Hook->>Queue: Append JSONL line
    Hook->>Queue: Append JSONL line
    Hook->>Queue: Append JSONL line
    
    Note over Processor,CLI: Processing Phase (Session End or Manual)
    Processor->>CLI: Execute queue command
    CLI->>Queue: Read all lines
    CLI->>Queue: Parse JSONL
    
    loop For each memory
        CLI->>Client: storeMemory(entry)
        Client->>API: POST /memory
        API-->>Client: {memory_id}
        Client-->>CLI: Success
    end
    
    CLI->>Queue: Delete file
    CLI-->>Processor: Complete